  "response": "Choosing a baby name is a special and meaningful decision. Here are some beautiful and unique baby boy names that start with \"Bh\":\n\n1. **Bhavesh** - Meaning \"lord of the world\" or \"god of the world\" in Sanskrit.\n2. **Bhavik** - Meaning \"devout\" or \"pious\" in Sanskrit.\n3. **Bharat** - Meaning \"India\" or \"descendant of King Bharata\" in Sanskrit.\n4. **Bhavan** - Meaning \"house\" or \"mansion\" in Sanskrit, often associated with a place of worship.\n5. **Bhuvan** - Meaning \"world\" or \"earth\" in Sanskrit.\n6. **Bharath** - A variant of Bharat, meaning \"India\" or \"descendant of King Bharata.\"\n7. **Bhaskar** - Meaning \"sun\" or \"radiant\" in Sanskrit.\n8. **Bhaumik** - Meaning \"earthly\" or \"related to the earth\" in Sanskrit.\n9. **Bhupen** - Meaning \"king of the earth\" in Sanskrit.\n10. **Bhuvanendra** - Meaning \"lord of the world\" in Sanskrit.\n\nThese names are deeply rooted in Indian culture and carry significant meanings, making them timeless and meaningful choices.",
